== Overview ==
The Hydron Core is the standard Hydron reactor. The Hydron system creates enormous amounts of power, but each reactor must be encased within a shell of Dion to absorb the pressure of the reaction thus making these devices extremely heavy.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Hydron Core Reactor can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.

